<h4 id="100">2.1.3. Setting up item lists</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can group items with the help of item lists and highlight them that way in the single item view of an item. Ceres supports the following item lists:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
