<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Provides a text widget for entering HTML and Javascript. In the widget, click on the <strong>&lt;/&gt;</strong> icon to open the code editor. Click <strong>Edit</strong> to change the paddings and margins of the widget and the appearance of the background colour.</p></td>
