<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>List</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Provides a list that serves as placeholder. Click <strong>Edit</strong> to add list entries and icons. You can define a target link for each list entry, so that you can link to external web pages or files.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Text</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Provides a text box. Click <strong>Edit</strong> to open the text editor. You can select the  colour for the text widget from the <strong>Appearance</strong> drop-down list. Activating the checkboxes <strong>Paddings</strong> and <strong>Margins</strong> provides additional formatting options for the widget.</p></td>
