<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter a meta title. <em>SEO tip</em>: Pay attention to the length of the title.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Meta description</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter a meta description (max. 350 characters). Search engines analyse the meta description. This makes it particularly important for the homepage.
<em>SEO tip</em>: The meta description should contain the most important content in one sentence.</p></td>
