<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Meta-Keywords</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter key words that potential customers are likely to enter into search engines and that relate to the content of the category.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Meta robots</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Choose between <strong>all</strong>, <strong>index</strong>, <strong>nofollow</strong>, <strong>noindex</strong> and <strong>nofollow, noindex</strong>. Search engine crawlers analyse the robot values. The values determine how the crawler deals with the page and any links on that page.<br>
<strong>all</strong> = Include the website of the category in the search engine index and follow links on the page.<br>
<strong>index</strong> = Add to search engine index.<br>
<strong>nofollow</strong> = Do not follow links on the page.<br>
